"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"20230611110006"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/20230611110006-20240612082518-467xyjq.png"},{"Type":"NodeLinkSpace"},{"Type":"NodeLinkTitle","Data":"图9.39：每一行的表面粗糙度从左到右递增。上面两行展示的是一种金色的金属材质，其中第一行在渲染的时候并没有使用Imageworks多次反弹项，而第二行在渲染的时候则使用了多次反弹项。二者之间的差异，对于表面粗糙度较高的球体而言最为明显。接下来的两行是黑色的电介质材质，其中第三行在渲染的时候没有使用多次反弹项，而第四行则使用了多次反弹项。第三行和第四行的差异更加细微，因为它们的镜面反射率要低得多。"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240612082535-g0itv70","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240612082535-g0itv70","updated":"20240625084123"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.9 次表面散射的BRDF模型"}]},{"ID":"20240612082731-4v1bnsr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240612082731-4v1bnsr","updated":"20240612084629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这一小节将讨论表明一下的折射光线会发生什么。这些折射光线经历了某种散射作用（scatter）和吸收作用（absorption）的组合，其中一部分光线最终会被重新发射回原始表面（9.1.4）。在本小节中，我们将重点讨论不透明电介质中的局部次表面散射，以及它们的BRDF模型。"}]},{"ID":"20240612084645-sdlqmin","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240612084645-sdlqmin","updated":"20240612084649"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里我们并不会讨论有关金属材质的话题，因为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"金属材质并没有任何明显的次表面光线作用"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（因为金属的对光线的吸收作用很强）。"}]},{"ID":"20240612084649-am3xafg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240612084649-am3xafg","updated":"20240612084712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"透明电介质材质以及表现出全局次表面散射的电介质材质将在14章讨论。"}]},{"ID":"20240625075128-o108ibr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240625075128-o108ibr","updated":"20240625084123"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.9.1 次表面反照率"}]},{"ID":"20240625080007-6y2aa6v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080007-6y2aa6v","updated":"20240625080143"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不透明电介质的次表面反照率（subsurface albedo）"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​指的是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"从表面逃逸的光线能量，与进入物质内部的光线能量之比"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240625080144-jzgnefe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080144-jzgnefe","updated":"20240625080201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的值在0（光线被全部吸收）到1（没有任何光线被吸收）之间，并且与波长有关，因此"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在渲染中被表示为一个RGB向量。"}]},{"ID":"20240625080202-4u0lr7v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080202-4u0lr7v","updated":"20240625080224"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于艺术家创作而言，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通常会被称为表面的漫反射颜色（diffuse color），就像是法线入射的菲涅尔反射率"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F_0"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，通常会被称为镜面颜色（specular color）一样。"}]},{"ID":"20240625080226-a4m3agp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080226-a4m3agp","updated":"20240625080511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于电介质而言，由于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"大部分光线都会透射进物质内部，而不是在表面上直接被反射出去，因此这些材质的次表面反照率"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-math text","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"通常会更加明亮，在视觉上要比高光颜色"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-math text","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F_0"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"更加重要"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。与表面的菲涅尔反射不同，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"光线在物质内部的吸收是一个独特的物理过程，因此"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-math text","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"通常具有与"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-math text","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F_0"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"不同的光谱分布"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（即不同的RGB颜色）"}]},{"ID":"20240625080434-cl640wr","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240625080434-cl640wr","updated":"20240625080532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240625080532-btpfbkh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080532-btpfbkh","updated":"20240625080532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例如：彩色塑料是由透明的基板和嵌入在其内部的颜料颗粒组成的，光线照射到彩色塑料表面上，所产生的镜面反射光线是无色的，而漫反射光线有一部分（特定波长）会被颜料颗粒吸收，因此剩余被反射出来的光线会具有某种颜色。比如我们能够看到在一个红色的塑料球上看到一个白色的高光。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240625080533-vk5rn42","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080533-vk5rn42","updated":"20240625080556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"次表面反照率可以被认为是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"光线吸收与光线散射之间“相互竞争”所产生的结果"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240625080549-pkzcwxz","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240625080549-pkzcwxz","updated":"20240625080617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240625080550-cx9e7so","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080550-cx9e7so","updated":"20240625080617"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这也就是为什么液体上的泡沫，要比液体本身亮得多的原因：起泡过程并不会改变液体对光线的吸收率，但是所产生的大量气液界面会大大增加光线的散射量，这使得大部分入射光线在被吸收之前，会先被散射出去，最终导致了较高的次表面反照率和明亮的材质外观。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240625080618-xg85cfl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240625080618-xg85cfl","updated":"20240625080635"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240625080619-n5ei179","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080619-n5ei179","updated":"20240625080635"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"新鲜的积雪是高反照率物质的另一个例子：新鲜的积雪十分蓬松，内部充满了空气，雪花颗粒与空气之间界面的散射量很大，吸收量很少，从而导致次表面反照率在可见光谱上可以达到0.8或者更大。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240625080635-u2b1osy","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240625080635-u2b1osy","updated":"20240625080645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240625080637-iw3kmhv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080637-iw3kmhv","updated":"20240625080645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白色油漆的次表面反照率要稍少小一些，约为0.7。日常生活中遇到的许多物质，例如混凝土、石头、土壤等，反照率大约在0.15 ~ 0.4之间。而煤炭是一种次表面反照率极低的物质，接近0.0。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240625080646-65a6xuc","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240625080646-65a6xuc","updated":"20240625080746"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240625080746-bpudnfs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080746-bpudnfs","updated":"20240625080746"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和液体泡沫的例子相反，许多物质在潮湿之后反而会变得更暗。如果一个材料表面是多孔的，那么水就会渗入到原本充满空气的空间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240625080743-yzs7i51","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080743-yzs7i51","updated":"20240625080743"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相比于空气的折射率，电介质材料的折射率要更加接近于水。表面两侧相对折射率的下降，会降低物体内部的散射率，这使得光线在逃逸出物质之前，需要传播的平均距离更长。这种变化会导致更多的光线被吸收，从而使得次表面反照率变得更暗[821]。"}]},{"ID":"20240625080747-slmby3l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080747-slmby3l","updated":"20240625080913"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当从真实世界的表面材质获取点值或者纹理时，从中分离镜面反射是十分重要的，这种提取操作可以通过精确控制光照和偏振滤光器[251, 952]来完成。为获得更加准确的颜色数据，还应当进行校准[1153]。"}]},{"ID":"20240625080917-8dyv3s3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625080917-8dyv3s3","updated":"20240625081037"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"并不是每个RGB三元组都代表一个合理（或者是物理上可能存在的）的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"值。对于任何波长的光线而言，它们的值永远都不能超过1，并且这些值的分布通常是相当平滑的。在设置"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的值时需要格外小心，避免指定那些不自然的、饱和且明亮的颜色。除了会"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"降低画面的真实感之外，在预计算全局光照的时候，这些不合理的颜色可能会导致过于明亮的二次反射"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Ref 11.5.1。"}]},{"ID":"20240625080947-bv6bado","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240625080947-bv6bado","updated":"20240625084123"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.9.2 次表面散射和粗糙的尺寸"}]},{"ID":"20240625081053-4jwi96u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625081053-4jwi96u","updated":"20240625081319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一些用于局部次表面散射的BRDF模型，考虑了表面粗糙度所带来的影响（通常使用了带有漫反射micro-BRDF"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f_{\\mu}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的微表面理论），而有些则没有这些影响。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"具体使用哪种类型的模型，并不是简单取决于表面有多粗糙（虽然这是一个常见的误解），正确的决定因素应当是表面不规则性与次表面散射距离的相对大小"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240625081330-ll124n7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625081330-ll124n7","updated":"20240625081338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"display: block;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240625081330-dc8gdo9.png"},{"Type":"NodeLinkSpace"},{"Type":"NodeLinkTitle","Data":"图9.40：具有相似NDF，但是微观几何尺度与次表面散射距离相对大小不同的三个表面。左上角：次表面散射距离小于表面不规则性；右上角：次表面散射距离大于表面不规则性。下方：展示了一个具有多种不同尺度粗糙度的微表面，图中红色虚线代表了其有效表面，它仅包含大于次表面散射距离的微观结构。"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: parent-style=\"display: block;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20240625081338-oil9leh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625081338-oil9leh","updated":"20240625081623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"如果次表面散射的距离都大于表面的不规则性"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（图9.40右上），那么在模拟次表面散射现象的时候，应该认为表面是平坦的，不会出现逆反射等效应。此时次表面散射对于微表面而言，并不是一个局部现象，因此无法使用微表面理论来进行描述。在这种情况下，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"应当使用一个光滑表面的漫反射模型"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240625081620-r93rr32","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625081620-r93rr32","updated":"20240625081807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而在其他中间情况下，即"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"表面在比散射距离更大或者更小的尺度上都具有一定的粗糙度，那么这时应当使用一个粗糙表面的漫反射模型，但是其有效表面（effective surface）只包含那些比散射距离更大的不规则性"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。在这种情况下，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"漫反射和镜面反射都可以使用微表面理论来进行建模，但是二者的粗糙度值是不同的：其中高光项将会使用一个基于实际表面粗糙度的值；而漫反射项将会使用一个较低的值，它基于的是有效表面的粗糙度"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240625081747-kjoaguf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625081747-kjoaguf","updated":"20240625081853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"观察尺度也与此相关，因为它决定了“微观几何”的具体含义。"}]},{"ID":"20240625081854-jeoaeyk","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240625081854-jeoaeyk","updated":"20240625081900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240625081855-l9yo8xa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625081855-l9yo8xa","updated":"20240625081900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例如：一个应当使用粗糙表面漫反射模型的经典例子是月球，因为它表现出了明显的逆反射效应。当我们从地球上观察月球的时候，观察尺度非常大，以至于月球表面上一个五英尺高的巨石都可以算是“微观几何”。因此，我们能够观察到粗糙表面的漫反射效应（例如后反射）也就并不奇怪了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240625081901-tqwiexq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240625081901-tqwiexq","updated":"20240730142153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.9.3 光滑表面的次表面模型"}]},{"ID":"20240625081931-34mbhjm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625081931-34mbhjm","updated":"20240625082711"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本小节我们将讨论光滑表面的次表面模型（smooth-surface subsurface model）。这些方法适用于对表面不规则性小于次表面散射距离的材质进行建模，这些材质的表面粗糙度并不会直接影响它们的漫反射着色，但是如果漫反射项和高光项是耦合的（本小节中一些模型是这样的），那么表面粗糙度可能会对漫反射着色产生间接影响。"}]},{"ID":"20240625082820-u9uq6as","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625082820-u9uq6as","updated":"20240625082853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实时渲染程序通常会使用Lambertian项来对局部次表面散射现象进行建模，在这种情况下，BRDF的漫反射项是次表面反照率"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除以"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\pi"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20240625082853-fn7g5sq","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240625082853-fn7g5sq","updated":"20240625082918"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=\\frac{\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}}}{\\pi}\n\\tag{9.61}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240625082900-qd2bsqn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625082900-qd2bsqn","updated":"20240625082934"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Lambertian模型并没有考虑到这样一个事实，即"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"表面反射的光线并不能用于次表面散射"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240625082934-d38vo4t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625082934-d38vo4t","updated":"20240625083009"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了对这个模型进行改进，应当在表面反射项（镜面反射项）和次表面反射项（漫反射项）之间进行能量权衡。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"菲涅尔效应表明，这种表面-次表面之间的能量权衡，应当随着入射光角 "},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-math text","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\theta_i"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"的变化而变化。随着光线入射角度（尤其是靠近掠射角度时）的增大，漫反射率会减小，镜面反射率会增大。"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实现这种平衡的最基本方法是，将漫反射项乘以1减去镜面项的菲涅尔部分（F项）[1626]。如果某个高光项是由平坦镜面所产生的话，那么对应产生的漫反射项为："}]},{"ID":"20240625083018-yrotx6d","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240625083018-yrotx6d","updated":"20240625083042"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=(1-F(\\mathbf{n}, \\mathbf{l})) \\frac{\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}}}{\\pi}\n\\tag{9.62}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240625083043-pyojb8n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083043-pyojb8n","updated":"20240625083051"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果镜面反射项是一个微表面BRDF项的话，那么对应产生的漫反射项为："}]},{"ID":"20240625083053-iqx6ent","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240625083053-iqx6ent","updated":"20240625083059"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=(1-F(\\mathbf{h}, \\mathbf{l})) \\frac{\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}}}{\\pi}\n\\tag{9.63}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240625083100-v341w0n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083100-v341w0n","updated":"20240625083341"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方程9.62最终会生成均匀分布的出射光线，因为这个BRDF的结果并不依赖于出射方向"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\mathbf{v}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这种光线行为是有一定道理的，因为光线在重新发射出表面之前，通常都会经历多次散射事件，因此其最终的出射方向将会是随机的。"}]},{"ID":"20240625083342-4rwu46l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083342-4rwu46l","updated":"20240625083400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而，存在有两个理由使得我们怀疑其实出射光线的分布并不是完全均匀的。"}]},{"ID":"20240625083401-tgz78xp","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240625083401-tgz78xp","updated":"20240625083413"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240625083402-jp6u9iq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240625083402-jp6u9iq","updated":"20240625083402"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240625083402-yqi3ygw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083402-yqi3ygw","updated":"20240625083407"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，由于方程9.62中的漫反射BRDF项会随光线入射方向的变化而变化，Helmholtz互易性意味着，它也会随着出射方向的变化而变化。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240625083409-nnreg5x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240625083409-nnreg5x","updated":"20240625083413"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240625083409-yn13lrm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083409-yn13lrm","updated":"20240625083413"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二，光线在最终射出表面的时候会发生折射，根据光线折射的性质，这些最终射出的光线会具有一定的方向性，即会偏向于某些方向。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240625083512-02lkpqd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083512-02lkpqd","updated":"20240625083539"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Shirley等人提出了一种用于平坦表面的耦合漫反射项，它解决了菲涅尔效应与表面-次表面反射之间的权衡问题，同时它还满足能量守恒和Helmholtz互易性[1627]。推导中假设菲涅尔反射使用了Schlick近似方法[1568]（方程9.16），其数学形式如下："}]},{"ID":"20240625083632-ju8mo59","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240625083632-ju8mo59","updated":"20240625083639"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=\\frac{21}{20 \\pi}\\left(1-F_{0}\\right) \\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}}\\left(1-\\left(1-(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{l})^{+}\\right)^{5}\\right)\\left(1-\\left(1-(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{v})^{+}\\right)^{5}\\right)\n\\tag{9.64}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240625083639-2nd76x5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083639-2nd76x5","updated":"20240625083706"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方程9.64只适用于镜面反射为完美菲涅尔镜面的表面。Ashikhmin和Shirley [77]提出了一个广义的版本，它可以用来计算一个可逆的（reciprocal）、低计算开销的漫反射项，并且它可以与任何高光项结合使用。Kelemen和Szirmay-Kalos [878]对其进行了进一步完善："}]},{"ID":"20240625083708-km80v7o","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240625083708-km80v7o","updated":"20240708194551"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}} \\frac{\\left(1-R_{\\mathrm{spec}}(\\mathbf{l})\\right)\\left(1-R_{\\mathrm{spec}}(\\mathbf{v})\\right)}{\\pi\\left(1-\\overline{R_{\\mathrm{spec}}}\\right)}\n\\tag{9.65}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240625083733-cmqd7u2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083733-cmqd7u2","updated":"20240625083747"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方程中的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{spec}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是高光项的定向反照率（directional albedo，详见章节9.3），而"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\overline{R_{\\mathrm{spec}}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"则是它在半球上的余弦加权平均值。值"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{spec}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以使用方程9.8或者方程9.9预计算出来，并将结果存储在一个查找表中。平均值"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\overline{R_{\\mathrm{spec}}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的计算方法与我们之前所遇到的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\overline{R_{\\mathrm{sF1}}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相同（方程9.57）。"}]},{"ID":"20240625083747-sr556u5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625083747-sr556u5","updated":"20240625084100"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方程9.65在形式上与方程9.56有一些明显的相似之处，这并不奇怪，因为Imageworks的多次弹射高光项，就是从Kelemen-Szirmay-Kalos耦合漫反射项中推导出来的。然而，二者之间有一个重要的区别：在这里我们使用的是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{spec}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而不是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{sF1}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，即使用了包含菲涅尔项、多次弹射高光项"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f_{ms}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（如果使用了的话）在内的、完整的镜面反射BRDF项的定向反照率。这种差异增加了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{spec}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查找表的维度，因为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"它不仅取决于粗糙度"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-math text","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\alpha"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"和仰角"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"inline-math text","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\theta"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"，还取决于菲涅尔反射率"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240625084047-bxwo8w3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625084047-bxwo8w3","updated":"20240625084123"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在Imageworks对Kelemen-Szirmay-Kalos耦合漫反射项的实现中，他们使用了一个三维查找表，其中的第三个维度是折射率[947]。他们发现，在积分中使用多次弹射项，可以使"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{spec}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"变得比"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{sF1}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更加平滑，因此"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"16\\times 16 \\times  16"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查找表很足够了，图9.41展示了相应的结果。"}]},{"ID":"20240625084136-gtiqtja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625084136-gtiqtja","updated":"20240625084152"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"display: block;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"20230611110136"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/20230611110136-20240625084135-ezgipid.png"},{"Type":"NodeLinkSpace"},{"Type":"NodeLinkTitle","Data":"图9.41：第一行和第三行图片展示了在一个Lambertian项中添加高光项的渲染结果。第二行和第四行图片使用了Kelemen-Szirmay-Kalos耦合漫反射项，并添加了一个相同的高光项。上面两行的粗糙度值要比下面两行低。在每一行中，粗糙度从左到右递增。"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: parent-style=\"display: block;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20240625084153-kdh8wrx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240625084153-kdh8wrx","updated":"20240625084329"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果BRDF使用Schlick Fresnel近似方法，但是不包含多次反弹高光项的话，那么"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F_0"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的值可以从积分中提取出来。这样我们就可以只使用一个二维的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{spec}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查找表，而不是Karis [861]所讨论的三维表。此外，Lazarov [999]提出了一个用于拟合"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"R_{\\mathrm{spec}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的解析函数，我们同样将系数"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F_0"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从积分中提取出来，从而对拟合函数进行简化。"}]},{"ID":"20240625084330-1smkhta","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240625084330-1smkhta","updated":"20240730143301"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.9.4 粗糙表面的次表面模型"}]},{"ID":"20240730142256-t9syoom","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730142256-t9syoom","updated":"20240730142256"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为迪士尼原则着色模型的一部分，Burley [214]引入了一个漫反射BRDF项，用于匹配被测材质的粗糙度效果："}]},{"ID":"20240730142310-z0a9kn2","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240730142310-z0a9kn2","updated":"20240730143007"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=\\chi^{+}(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{l}) \\chi^{+}(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{v}) \\frac{\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}}}{\\pi}\\left(\\left(1-k_{\\mathrm{ss}}\\right) f_{\\mathrm{d}}+1.25 k_{\\mathrm{ss}} f_{\\mathrm{ss}}\\right)\n\\tag{9.66}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240730142256-us4c6bl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730142256-us4c6bl","updated":"20240730142256"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中："}]},{"ID":"20240730142303-sehbop4","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240730142303-sehbop4","updated":"20240730143007"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\begin{aligned} \nf_{\\mathrm{d}} \u0026 =\\left(1+\\left(F_{\\mathrm{D} 90}-1\\right)(1-\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{l})^{5}\\right)\\left(1+\\left(F_{\\mathrm{D} 90}-1\\right)(1-\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{v})^{5}\\right), \\\\[1mm]\n F_{\\mathrm{D} 90} \u0026 =0.5+2 \\sqrt{\\alpha}(\\mathbf{h} \\cdot \\mathbf{l})^{2}, \\\\\n  f_{\\mathrm{Ss}} \u0026 =\\left(\\frac{1}{(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{l})(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{v})}-0.5\\right) F_{\\mathrm{SS}}+0.5, \\\\\n   F_{\\mathrm{SS}} \u0026 =\\left(1+\\left(F_{\\mathrm{SS} 90}-1\\right)(1-\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{l})^{5}\\right)\\left(1+\\left(F_{\\mathrm{SS} 90}-1\\right)(1-\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{v})^{5}\\right), \\\\[1mm]\n    F_{\\mathrm{SS} 90} \u0026 =\\sqrt{\\alpha}(\\mathbf{h} \\cdot \\mathbf{l})^{2},\\end{aligned}\n    \\tag{9.67}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240730142256-o7u4epw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730142256-o7u4epw","updated":"20240730142338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方程9.67中的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\alpha"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是镜面粗糙度，在各向异性的情况下，则使用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\alpha_x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":" \\alpha_y "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"之间的中间值。这个方程通常被称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"迪斯尼漫反射模型"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（Disney diffuse model）。"}]},{"ID":"20240730142329-dilpyug","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730142329-dilpyug","updated":"20240730142427"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"次表面项"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的灵感来自于Hanrahan-Krueger BRDF [662]，用于作为对远处物体的全局次表面散射现象的廉价近似。这个漫反射模型会基于用户控制的参数"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"k_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，将"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f_{ss}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与粗糙漫反射项"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f_{d}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"混合在一起。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-7ntdvmf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-7ntdvmf","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"迪士尼漫反射模型被广泛应用于电影"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"214]和游戏"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"214]（尽管没有次表面项）中。完整的迪斯尼漫反射BRDF还包含一个光泽（sheen）项，这主要是为了对纤维织物进行建模，同时也有助于补偿因缺乏多次弹射高光项而造成的能量损失。有关迪士尼光泽项的内容将在章节9.10中进行讨论。几年后，Burley提出了一个更新后的模型"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"215]，旨在对全局次表面散射的渲染技术进行整合。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-c2ujroh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-c2ujroh","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由于迪斯尼漫反射模型使用了与镜面BRDF相同的粗糙度参数，因此在对某些材质进行建模的时候，可能会遇到困难，详见图9.40。然而，可以通过一个很小的修改，从而使用一个单独的漫反射粗糙度值。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-56zbqqq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-56zbqqq","updated":"20240730143301"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其他大多数粗糙表面的漫反射BRDF都是基于微表面理论开发的，它们具有不同的NDF、micro-BRDF"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f_{\\mu}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以及masking-shadowing函数"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_2"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"其中最著名的模型是由Oren和Nayar提出的[1337]。Oren-Nayar BRDF使用了Lambertian的micro-BRDF、球面高斯NDF以及Torrance-Sparrow“V-cavity”的masking-shadowing函数"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。完整形式的BRDF模型了对二次反弹也进行了建模。Oren和Nayar还在他们的论文中引入了一个简化的“定性”模型。多年来，人们提出了一些对Oaren-Nayar模型的改进方法"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"573]，包括对“定性”模型进行优化调整，使其在不增加额外成本的前提下，尽可能地接近完整模型"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"504]；以及将micro-BRDF更改为一个更加精确的光滑表面漫反射模型"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"574, 1899]。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-m7vmv0z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-m7vmv0z","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Oren-Nayar模型假设了一个全新的微表面，与当前镜面模型所使用的微表面相比，它具有完全不同的法线分布和masking-shadowing函数。利用各向同性的GGX NDF和高度相关的Smith masking-shadowing函数，可以推导出两种不同的漫反射微表面模型。第一个模型是由Gotanda "},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"574]提出的，他使用了方程9.64所描述的镜面耦合漫反射项来作为micro-BRDF，再对通用的微表面方程（方程9.26）进行数值积分，最后使用一个解析函数来对数值积分的数据进行拟合。Gotanda提出的BRDF并没有考虑微表面之间的相互反射，并且拟合函数也相对复杂。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-dbu0vz9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-dbu0vz9","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用与Gotanda BRDF相同的NDF、masking-shadowing函数和micro-BRDF，Hammon "},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"657]对BRDF进行了数值模拟，同时将相互反射考虑在内。他指出，相互反射对于这种微表面结构而言十分重要，对于粗糙表面来说，相互反射大约占据了总反射中的一半。Hammon发现第二次反弹几乎包含了所有丢失的能量（即考虑更多的反弹次数，对最终结果的贡献并不大），因此他使用了两次反弹模拟的数据。 此外，可能是因为添加了相互反射，使得数据变得更加平滑，因此Hammon能够使用一个相当简单的函数，来对模拟结果进行拟合，最终的数学表达如下："}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-dhdw2c0","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-dhdw2c0","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=\\chi^{+}(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{l}) \\chi^{+}(\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{v}) \\frac{\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}}}{\\pi}\\left(\\left(1-\\alpha_{g}\\right) f_{\\mathrm{smooth}}+\\alpha_{g} f_{\\mathrm{rough}}+\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}} f_{\\mathrm{multi}}\\right)\n\\tag{9.68}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-gn9hfa5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-gn9hfa5","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中："}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-8e98720","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-8e98720","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\begin{aligned} f_{\\text {smooth }} \u0026 =\\frac{21}{20}\\left(1-F_{0}\\right)\\left(1-(1-\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{l})^{5}\\right)\\left(1-(1-\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{v})^{5}\\right), \\\\ f_{\\text {rough }} \u0026 =k_{\\text {facing }}\\left(0.9-0.4 k_{\\text {facing }}\\right)\\left(\\frac{0.5+\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{h}}{\\mathbf{n} \\cdot \\mathbf{h}}\\right), \\\\ k_{\\text {facing }} \u0026 =0.5+0.5(\\mathbf{l} \\cdot \\mathbf{v}), \\\\ f_{\\text {multi }} \u0026 =0.3641 \\alpha_{g},\\end{aligned}\n\\tag{9.69}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-a09g7yd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-a09g7yd","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方程中的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\alpha_{g}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是GGX镜面粗糙度。为了清楚起见，这里所使用术语与Hammon的陈述略有不同。请注意，方程9.69中的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":" f_{\\text {smooth }}  "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，其实就是方程9.64中不含"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}} / \\pi"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因子的耦合漫反射BRDF，因为这个因子被包含在了方程9.68中。Hammon讨论了一些“混合”BRDF，即使用其他光滑表面的漫反射BRDF来替代"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":" f_{\\text {smooth }}  "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，从而提高性能表现，或者改进旧着色模型下的资产兼容性。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-bvajwpu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-bvajwpu","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总的来说，尽管Hammon并没有给出与测量数据的比较，但是他提出漫反射BRDF的计算开销很低，并且建立在可靠的理论原理之上。需要注意的是，表面不规则性大于散射距离的这个假设，是BRDF推导的基础，这可能会对它能够准确建模的材质类型有所限制，详见图9.40。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-i5deb2q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-i5deb2q","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方程9.61中展示的简单Lambertian项仍然被许多实时渲染程序所采用，除了较低的计算成本之外，与其他的漫反射模型相比，它可以更加容易地和间接烘焙光照一起使用；与更加复杂的着色模型相比，二者之间的视觉差异通常是不易察觉的"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"251, 861]。然而，对于真实感的持续追求，正在推动精确模型的广泛使用。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-nsomgyq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-nsomgyq","updated":"20240730143736"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.10 布料的BRDF模型"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-qlcmq7d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-qlcmq7d","updated":"20240730143404"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"布料往往具有不同于其他类型材质的微观几何结构，根据织物类型的不同，它可能还会具有高度重复的编织微观结构、从表面垂直突出的圆柱体（线），又或是二者都有。由于布料表面独特的特征外观，因此"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color4);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"通常需要使用专门的着色模型来进行渲染，这些独特外观包括：各向异性的镜面高光，粗糙散射[919]（光线在突出的、半透明的纤维中发生散射，从而导致边缘明亮的效果）， 甚至颜色也会随着观察方向的变化而变化（这是由织物中不同颜色的线所引起的）"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color4);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-oq74f9d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-oq74f9d","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除了BRDF之外，大多数织物还具有高频空间变化，这也是生成令人信服的布料材质的关键因素"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"825]，如图9.42所示。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-a1azabd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-a1azabd","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"图9.42：一种使用《神秘海域4》布料系统的材质。左上方的球体使用了标准的BRDF，它具有GGX微表面镜面反射和Lambertian漫反射。上部中间的球体使用了纤维织物的BRDF。其他每个球体上都添加了不同类型的逐像素变化，从左上到右下分别是：织物编织细节，织物老化程度，细节瑕疵和小皱纹。"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/20230611110158-20240730143051-wdq237b.png"},{"Type":"NodeLinkSpace"},{"Type":"NodeLinkTitle","Data":"图9.42：一种使用《神秘海域4》布料系统的材质。左上方的球体使用了标准的BRDF，它具有GGX微表面镜面反射和Lambertian漫反射。上部中间的球体使用了纤维织物的BRDF。其他每个球体上都添加了不同类型的逐像素变化，从左上到右下分别是：织物编织细节，织物老化程度，细节瑕疵和小皱纹。"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-vbzx1nf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-vbzx1nf","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"布料的BRDF模型主要分为三大类：根据观察建立的经验模型、基于微表面理论的模型、微圆柱体模型。我们将从每个类别中分别举出一些值得注意的例子。"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-tud0xpr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-tud0xpr","updated":"20240730143736"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.10.1 经验布料模型"}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-hdpb6x6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-hdpb6x6","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在游戏《神秘海域2》"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"631]中，布料表面使用了以下的漫反射BRDF项："}]},{"ID":"20240730143153-ess33r1","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20240730143153-ess33r1","updated":"20240730143153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"f_{\\mathrm{diff}}(\\mathbf{l}, \\mathbf{v})=\\frac{\\rho_{\\mathrm{ss}}}{\\pi}\\left(k_{\\mathrm{rim}}\\left((\\mat